</tr>
<tr>
<td width="100%"><font size="2">On Wednesday, August 6th, at 3AM Pacific, (-7:00 UTC), all EverQuest servers will be brought down for a scheduled update. The estimated downtime is 3 hours. <br><br>- The SOE Game Operations Team </font><br><br></td>
